query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('serverfault')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('bind',
'dovecot',
'hardware',
'hp',
'php-fpm',
'redirect',
'router',
'scripting',
'sql-server-2008',
'tcp',
'virtual-machines');
